    "description": "Deco Deck is a new logic puzzle from the creator of Semantle and Surfwords.  Your goal is to link the cards on the board in connected groups of five, such that each group makes a valid &quot;hand&quot;.  Hands are: straights, flushes, full houses, five of a kind, and rainbows. To win, every card on the board must be part of a hand.  Each puzzle has only one solution. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296050/extras/1c4230d2fd23fe026632a3dc62d5423a.poster.avif?t=1683980715\" width=594 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296050/extras/1c4230d2fd23fe026632a3dc62d5423a.webm?t=1683980715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296050/extras/1c4230d2fd23fe026632a3dc62d5423a.mp4?t=1683980715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Deco Deck includes four puzzles every day, and 48 additional puzzles every month.  You can access the complete archives of all past daily and monthly puzzles.<br><br>A colorblind accessibility mode is available.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296050/extras/cc10e380c39b261dbc1d718ebf8016f9.poster.avif?t=1683980715\" width=594 height=379 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296050/extras/cc10e380c39b261dbc1d718ebf8016f9.webm?t=1683980715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
